{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1931, "height": 2659, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [113, 707, 188, 1380], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三六七", "block_bbox": [126, 1996, 175, 2113], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "另殿供奉，一殿之内，灵楼居中正位、六祖左右偏位之故。大殿东、西两边墙上彩绘二十四孝之十二孝图（祠堂内相传清代有二十四孝全图，今除去不合时宜及迷信之部分），东为大舜耕田、文帝侍疾、啮指心痛、芦衣顺母、子路负米、行佣供母；西为闻雷泣墓、陆绩怀橘、亲涤溺器、弃官寻母、恣蚊饱血、扇枕温衾。殿宇之檐间、栋梁皆以油漆，彩绘焕然。另，祠堂之朽坏之木也以替换，屋脊之雕刻、屋瓦也整治一新。2008年农历十月初一日，杜氏宗族云集祠堂，举行了盛大的杜氏宗祠、石旌柱修缮完工仪式和祭祖大典。", "block_bbox": [283, 263, 1741, 714], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "2.宗祠内祖像文字", "block_bbox": [814, 805, 1194, 852], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏远祖——尧", "block_bbox": [369, 943, 661, 985], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "尧，祁姓，伊祁氏，名放勋，黄帝五世孙，上古五帝之一，又称“帝尧”、“唐尧”、“陶唐氏”。\n", "block_bbox": [289, 1010, 1741, 1120], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏远祖——刘累", "block_bbox": [370, 1143, 702, 1183], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "刘累，尧帝后裔。始封于刘，后为夏王孔甲驯龙，封“御龙氏”。其后裔别立杜氏，是为杜氏、刘氏共祖。\n", "block_bbox": [290, 1207, 1744, 1315], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏始祖——杜伯", "block_bbox": [370, 1339, 704, 1380], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "尧帝后裔刘累之后，周代始封于唐（在今山西），成王时迁封于杜（今陕西长安县曲江乡三兆村南），因号“唐杜氏”，杜伯为得姓之祖，宣王时被冤杀。不久国灭，子孙以国为氏。\n", "block_bbox": [287, 1402, 1745, 1573], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏名人——杜预", "block_bbox": [369, 1598, 703, 1638], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜预（222~284），字元凯，西晋征南大将军、司隶校尉，封当阳侯。曾平灭吴国，修订历法，注解《左传》，人称“杜武库”；在地方任职时，惠及百姓，人称“杜父”。\n", "block_bbox": [287, 1662, 1742, 1837], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏名人——杜如晦", "block_bbox": [369, 1858, 744, 1900], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜如晦（585~630），字克明，唐代文学馆十八学士之首、凌烟阁二十四功臣之一。与房玄龄并称“房谋杜断”，功定社稷，致“贞观之治”，封莱国公，为唐代四大贤相之一。\n", "block_bbox": [288, 1926, 1742, 2104], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏名人—杜甫", "block_bbox": [370, 2127, 707, 2170], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜甫（712~770），字子美，号“少陵野老”，唐代伟大诗人。官至左拾遗、检校工部员外郎。其诗反映历史，世号“诗史”。艺术成就达现实主义顶峰，人称“诗圣”。\n", "block_bbox": [287, 2194, 1742, 2377], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9704906940460205, "coordinate": [283.38690185546875, 263.701904296875, 1741.161376953125, 714.874755859375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9494646191596985, "coordinate": [287.5931396484375, 1662.896484375, 1742.4398193359375, 1837.41064453125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9485340118408203, "coordinate": [287.82037353515625, 2194.61376953125, 1742.121826171875, 2377.13525390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9472131729125977, "coordinate": [288.14691162109375, 1926.299072265625, 1742.093994140625, 2104.20703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9388476014137268, "coordinate": [287.67327880859375, 1402.787841796875, 1745.197998046875, 1573.78271484375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9062186479568481, "coordinate": [289.69769287109375, 1010.8429565429688, 1741.982666015625, 1120.940673828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9039363265037537, "coordinate": [290.14312744140625, 1207.7607421875, 1744.212890625, 1315.69775390625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7654405236244202, "coordinate": [369.25164794921875, 943.9820556640625, 661.5598754882812, 985.8729248046875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7542681097984314, "coordinate": [814.655029296875, 805.393310546875, 1194.202880859375, 852.583740234375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7338798642158508, "coordinate": [370.9419860839844, 2127.79052734375, 707.5848388671875, 2170.21142578125]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7280597686767578, "coordinate": [370.07373046875, 1339.8037109375, 704.572998046875, 1380.12109375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7164868116378784, "coordinate": [369.6819763183594, 1598.174560546875, 703.9327392578125, 1638.29150390625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7148222923278809, "coordinate": [370.18206787109375, 1143.64892578125, 702.6679077148438, 1183.94287109375]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6901152729988098, "coordinate": [369.0151672363281, 1858.6588134765625, 744.949462890625, 1900.2769775390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.4492557644844055, "coordinate": [126.71161651611328, 1996.88720703125, 175.638916015625, 2113.92138671875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.31663936376571655, "coordinate": [113.49348449707031, 707.8429565429688, 188.15098571777344, 1380.055908203125]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[294, 263], [1738, 264], [1738, 311], [294, 310]], [[296, 333], [1737, 333], [1737, 377], [296, 377]], [[295, 400], [1735, 400], [1735, 445], [295, 445]], [[294, 467], [173